These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: whist, poker
There 2 different types of food: carrot, orange
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, aquamarine
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
2. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
3. the person eating orange is the person playing whist##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Game      | whist  | poker   |
| Food   | orange     | carrot   |
| Color         | aquamarine | lavender |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks | skydiving    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse
House: palace, cape-cod
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, gospel
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the palace house is the fan of gospel##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Job          | entrepreneur     | nurse |
| House   | cape-cod | palace  |
| Sport           | lacrosse         | handball     |
| Music-Genre     | soul   | gospel    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, nigerian
City: hannover, miami
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the nigerian##1
3. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Game    | monopoly     | bridge |
| Nationality         | nigerian | malaysian    |
| City         | hannover         | miami        |
| Cigar   | chaman         | ritmeester    |

