.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
City: boston, london
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, van
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, biathlon
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, march
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| City      | london     | boston |
| Transport          | van   | motorbike  |
| Sport         | soccer | biathlon     |
| Birthday   | july  | march         |

