.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-12::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, rat
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, purple
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, juice
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker
1. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Pet         | rat   | frog |
| Color           | mauve | purple    |
| Beverage   | tea      | juice         |
| Game         | mah-jongg   | poker |

